Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2148年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平本应到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自遥远外空间的敌人 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在北极与之决战后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军方势力却仍然在继续着战争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管大多数人并不希望战争持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以彻底消灭敌人为目的的作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然在世界各地被实行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这正是新的战斗的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了 这是一骑咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看上去好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 B桌两份套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生 加餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来两份一骑咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 沟口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以在菜单里加上我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你是这里的招牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生 外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到亚尔维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(343,438)}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明还有祭奠的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在进行本年度U计划的最终确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年在盂兰盆舞会中将有些许变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我来杯蜜瓜苏打和一骑蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要柠檬茶和一骑布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑咖喱套餐和焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一起说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边明明很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校开不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会在这开是惯例啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤会长不是没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议已经全权委托给副会长我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的会长还是在老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光书记的活增加了 好累的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表扬下我嘛 远见学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晖 要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要黑咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像个大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给Chocolate也来点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保先生 要开始准备祭奠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要喝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没喝呢 剑司君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从完成Fafner的维修以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个劲儿地喝个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是多亏了小楯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了空号的4台以外 连13号机都可以用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连损伤惨重的Mark Funf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是完好无损的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是自己儿子驾驶过的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定无论如何都想修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有仇恨以外的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我一同去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们包括原人类军成员在内对系统的操作熟练度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都达到了规定标准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题就在于布伦希尔德系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(342,438)}Brynhildr
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当于岛上的环境维持系统的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入成长期了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给成长中的核心注入力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生态系和食物系统以及岛民的健康等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个岛都将会发生混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 所罗门有反应的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在北极将敌人的中枢星核给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\pos(405,438)}Mir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还能继续活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定敌方的星核已经变成了别的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们的星核变成了岛上的大气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说敌方的核心也产生了相同的物质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是个未知数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续对所罗门的解析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 只能祈愿这份和平能持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 今早捉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锯锹形甲虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深山锹形甲虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎天牛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多事情想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算收拾完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见你就先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还有准备工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等到沟口先生回来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明亮的地方基本能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一会儿见 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被蹂躏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他心中充满了痛苦和仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是场赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会传达给你最后的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万不得已的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从11号门走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会回到你所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 刚才有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艘很大很大的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽画得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有更大的船和山哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有块很大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽 差不多该换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 只有美羽不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大船要来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶已经先去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去祭奠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经准备好了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么站着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看来能走着去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 咲良 你变重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是走着去算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑 玩笑而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了保先生的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的灯笼都向上游飘去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除一部分防护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候 我们的名字也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样被人们记载下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁范围内有活动体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 从西面来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是场赌局 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…核心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11号门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据对照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军 战略运输船B-29
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫描反应为零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主…操
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是你所期盼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备迎击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方形态为斯芬克斯A型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\pos(360,438)}Sphinx
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner 抓紧准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布伦希尔德系统异常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁减弱 要被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞄准了核心的成长期来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Sein 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(376,438)}Stand by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方正向龙宫岛本部进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Sein 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之洞1号门和6号门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(226,438)}Nighthre
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击路线畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是总士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…Festum吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然使用了人类的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根…根本性的不同战术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员出现剧烈的同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援的Fafner 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 就在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方已消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你躺着休息就行了 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警报…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有敌人 是岛在移动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁固定 解除镜面伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获取线路信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距自动航行启动还有两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始龙宫岛将离开停泊点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据上空测得的现象来规划逃脱路线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 即将转为战时态势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须做好对敌人进一步的进攻的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位的智慧与汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner的特征是无需操作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与机体同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受变性意识 就是接受自己变化的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 Mark Funf
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互间用机体型号称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是Fafner Fafner就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗 Mark Neun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zehn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见…前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晖…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听得见噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zwalf
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么 小晖…开口了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwalf 快回话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:21:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持各自的CROSSING
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是疼痛还是恐惧都由全员承受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶Fafner越久 同化现象就更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会马上就变得无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员适应性证实完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据现在的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认最合适的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良 为什么自己提出要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄美…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要让我拥有这样的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是整备工作班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Dreizehn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都还没有驾驶过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专属于你的第13号机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有用头去攻击的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是变性意识引发的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话 需要些预想外的装备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CROSSING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑一直处于CROSSING状态
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与正处在敌方那边的总士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两年间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持着联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象还尚未明确
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像与别的激剧的负荷有关联
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的负荷…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Sein有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那犹如同化现象的聚集体一般的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于过于特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的驾驶员都无法驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让一骑去驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在强烈的同化现象下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋庸置疑会丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人船那边如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船内发现的生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门断定为斯芬克斯型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身体组织类似于核型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他没有染色体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是人类的仿制品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和袭击岛的是同一类种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船本身没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从自动操纵的记录来看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船是直奔着岛来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说漂到这里并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据的大部分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来自于人类军对敌军新变种的分析资料
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅拥有强大的同化能力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拥有模仿人类兵器的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军称其为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.89,0:24:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧洛斯型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.89,0:24:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(318,438)}Euros
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.76,0:24:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是召唤暴风雨的神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.90,0:24:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是接下来要从战斗中获取敌人资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.03,0:24:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还发现了些奇怪的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.79,0:24:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被推荐对这个航行的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实施SC CODE级的情报公开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.30,0:24:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SC CODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把岛上的核心和星核的数据对人公开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 是要和星核同样机密的某些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.99,0:24:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.79,0:25:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.06,0:25:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作数据的人是谁也不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.26,0:25:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上空的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.06,0:25:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.33,0:25:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的因果关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.01,0:25:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤学长真的好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是故意输给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.31,0:25:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为的是让我们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.92,0:25:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能说话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上Fafner后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.90,0:25:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又觉得能说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.43,0:25:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是父亲和母亲曾乘坐过并且消失的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.55,0:25:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想乘坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.02,0:25:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上Zero Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.21,0:25:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不管坐什么都只会拖后腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.42,0:25:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.72,0:25:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.70,0:25:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太任性了吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.78,0:26:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨打受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.33,0:26:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.77,0:26:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不知道互助
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.69,0:26:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 大家都会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.69,0:26:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让这种事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.91,0:26:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.62,0:26:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不用
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.06,0:26:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.11,0:26:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.48,0:26:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.33,0:26:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就已经不嫌麻烦既照顾小楯先生又照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.77,0:26:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是担心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.04,0:26:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.09,0:26:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小守的去世也不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体会这样也不是任何人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道你深感自责
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.02,0:26:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.10,0:26:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我跟你一起分担吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.68,0:26:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.99,0:26:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.07,0:27:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在和人类的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故乡消失在核武器的火焰中时的后遗症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.51,0:27:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为岛上的星核病情得以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.37,0:27:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心的成长期又遭受敌军的来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.27,0:27:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致人工生态圈机能的衰退
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.11,0:27:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心要是撑过了成长期
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.68,0:27:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我一定会找出治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.43,0:27:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被岛救了这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.66,0:27:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多大的恩惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（战时停业中）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.88,0:28:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰炸加上炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.87,0:28:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在为着陆作准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人类一样攻击过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.03,0:28:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么对付的方法就要多少有多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.72,0:28:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.64,0:28:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后援的Fafner 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.92,0:28:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gobain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.48,0:28:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.60,0:28:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是经过改良的Nothung-model
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.32,0:29:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会这么轻易被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.26,0:29:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挡下来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.87,0:29:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.19,0:29:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体内藏的星核的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.23,0:29:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能防御敌人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.61,0:29:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己和机体 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.24,0:30:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往你那边去了 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.71,0:30:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.79,0:30:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.68,0:31:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.53,0:31:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.00,0:31:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.83,0:31:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.32,0:31:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔维斯内部出现Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.30,0:31:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.98,0:31:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.67,0:31:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.97,0:32:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛正在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.74,0:32:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.78,0:32:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.26,0:32:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我和他们交涉的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.96,0:32:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人^
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.42,0:32:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.67,0:32:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.20,0:32:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.34,0:32:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.06,0:32:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.11,0:32:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快投降吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.10,0:33:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.35,0:33:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不要一个人战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.63,0:33:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有人因为你而丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.80,0:33:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要像守学长那样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.70,0:33:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.89,0:33:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定是要说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.69,0:33:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.75,0:33:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太在意了都不能战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.70,0:33:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人会说些什么很明显啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.18,0:33:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厌恶 憎恨什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.33,0:33:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这些可解决不掉对方
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.15,0:33:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬才不会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.38,0:33:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.52,0:33:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.96,0:33:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.97,0:33:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是第一次作战有些兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:33:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打倒了4个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.16,0:34:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要是不逃的话还能再干掉几个的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.32,0:34:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要是能来更多点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.13,0:34:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得很享受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起剑司学长我更强
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.64,0:34:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 被嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.25,0:34:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了看我怎么教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.50,0:34:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就表扬他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.14,0:34:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用糖和鞭子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.13,0:34:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你觉得我们赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发出返回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.09,0:34:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.17,0:34:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是来主操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.66,0:34:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然面向全岛民播出
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.44,0:34:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是煽动民众的不安情绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.66,0:34:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁的做法就是这种愚顽方式的情报公开
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.55,0:34:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺有效的这招
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.33,0:34:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.24,0:34:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被你同化的人的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.21,0:34:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.53,0:34:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据皆城总士的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.85,0:35:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在你们的语言中表达我的存在就是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.50,0:35:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们说话需要有个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.32,0:35:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是皆城总士让你上船的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.33,0:35:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我这么希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.07,0:35:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像想传达什么给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.20,0:35:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上不是有他的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.41,0:35:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个数据是来自于皆城总士的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.50,0:35:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他不来岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.66,0:35:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为巨大的火焰的缘故…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.78,0:35:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们人类干的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.20,0:35:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴们也正为此痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.08,0:35:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军的…核攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.60,0:35:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.89,0:35:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为巨大的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.69,0:35:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星核已经不愿再获新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.54,0:35:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才作为代替诞生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.48,0:35:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.68,0:35:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的星核并没有消灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁叔叔 哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.57,0:35:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 分成了好几份
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.12,0:35:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.12,0:35:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我能问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.88,0:35:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.11,0:35:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.31,0:36:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有过天空很美的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.61,0:36:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.33,0:36:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.98,0:36:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.23,0:36:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.65,0:36:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.78,0:36:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用你们的读心能力
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.60,0:36:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来读取我们的思考吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.93,0:36:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.08,0:36:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是觉得天空很美我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.18,0:36:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.16,0:36:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止战争
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再增加疼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.45,0:36:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.32,0:36:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.74,0:36:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和你们的核心同化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.29,0:36:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.36,0:36:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需战争
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的星核能和我们的星核同化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.43,0:36:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为给我们带来痛楚和死的恐惧的正是这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.45,0:36:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要把我们和你们的痛楚一同消去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想消灭你们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.55,0:36:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.97,0:36:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 和谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.93,0:36:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类以及我们的其他种族
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.85,0:36:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.45,0:37:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把大家的战斗的力量全都夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.88,0:37:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.79,0:37:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会变得和平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.85,0:37:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想叫我现在立马接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.28,0:37:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答晚些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要你们大家一起决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.89,0:37:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.56,0:37:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴们还在痛苦中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.76,0:37:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这样下去 你们的核心会死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.74,0:37:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的天空被我们的星核占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.60,0:37:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个会毁了你们的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前你貌似会先死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.14,0:37:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的对话 还可以继续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.77,0:37:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.31,0:37:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一骑咖喱是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴求对话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.32,0:37:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出共同战线来解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还提到维持和平
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.34,0:37:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.05,0:37:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是条与世为敌的毁灭之路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.63,0:37:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说要跟别的种族战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.90,0:38:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击岛的仅仅是欧洛斯型这特殊的种族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.85,0:38:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人分成了好几个种族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.15,0:38:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少是实话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.70,0:38:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作数据是总士这点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.08,0:38:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法确认呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.02,0:38:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在核心的状态被敌人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.84,0:38:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公开SC CODE的意义何在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人对上空的情况很明确
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.77,0:38:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空会剥夺核心的生命这点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.39,0:38:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.02,0:38:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上敌人攻击的负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.31,0:38:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会威胁到核心的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.14,0:38:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这需要全岛民的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.96,0:38:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum会回归于尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的身体是由硅构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是土不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.67,0:38:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是不是也在寻找归宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.49,0:38:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.88,0:38:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.99,0:38:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然曾经失去过
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.88,0:38:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.25,0:39:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.61,0:39:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和沟口先生说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.93,0:39:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 从谁那听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.74,0:39:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见说你脸色不好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.12,0:39:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.30,0:39:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会保护岛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.24,0:39:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以爸爸就做自己喜欢的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.49,0:39:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.08,0:39:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起住在这里什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和远见老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么好笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.73,0:39:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住到Mark Sein里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.18,0:39:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已的话就那么干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.14,0:39:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.30,0:39:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里无论什么时候都能作为你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.61,0:39:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛还不能交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.30,0:39:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不用道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.14,0:39:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么看那个来主操
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.58,0:39:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.05,0:40:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.36,0:40:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.16,0:40:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士在他身上下了赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.63,0:40:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士为了保护这座岛 让那艘船来了岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.86,0:40:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么觉得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.09,0:40:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚 但是能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.97,0:40:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是消耗生命算不上是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.10,0:40:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去和他对话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剩下的时间里 寻找出拯救岛的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.89,0:40:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.81,0:40:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想灭了岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.24,0:41:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.54,0:41:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zehn
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.86,0:41:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全都消灭噢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.08,0:41:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.10,0:41:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你和总士
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.23,0:41:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想来这
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.38,0:41:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城总士曾在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.95,0:41:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他回归原处
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.24,0:41:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以穿着总士的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.67,0:41:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.42,0:41:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.54,0:41:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.23,0:41:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能取回他的存在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.23,0:41:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:41:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你交谈我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.80,0:42:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这座岛 让大家痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.02,0:42:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而觉得交谈很愉快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.63,0:42:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑在恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.54,0:42:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 只是在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.44,0:42:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对憎恨和怒火不太了解
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.21,0:42:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想这么痛苦的话 就按我说的话做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.00,0:42:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夺取核心的话 为什么现在不下手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.77,0:42:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想和你们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.39,0:42:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让你们的星核停手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.60,0:42:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 我没有那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是停过一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.01,0:42:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是让我来说明下目的才回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.22,0:42:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.13,0:42:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你们的手指一样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.38,0:42:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指无法命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.41,0:42:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.32,0:42:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.86,0:42:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回船上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.35,0:42:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如我的岛一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.70,0:42:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那船上有你的星核吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.69,0:42:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你是不是在想攻击我们的船
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.38,0:42:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保护这座岛的话就这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.67,0:43:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城总士说要这么做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.25,0:43:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.77,0:43:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还听得到他的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.21,0:43:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.38,0:43:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让他消失 我已经竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.27,0:43:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…保护总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.82,0:43:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给它最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.51,0:43:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认消灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.51,0:43:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击敌人时产生的物质
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.82,0:43:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给系统带来了重大的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.54,0:43:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要毁掉核心的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.24,0:43:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那孩子交谈的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.11,0:44:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起创造新的道路 史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.94,0:44:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.79,0:44:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.32,0:44:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SC CODE 和星核一样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.92,0:44:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被岛拯救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.63,0:44:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只是有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.61,0:44:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.49,0:44:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来人 去连续急救组
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.26,0:44:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急救组 请火速来格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.44,0:44:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去因星核以及核武器引起的污染
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.14,0:44:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计今后绝大多数岛民会出现病症
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本这是为了与Fafner一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.00,0:44:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于人工催化同化现象的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.38,0:44:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.04,0:44:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已别无他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.16,0:44:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 千鹤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.38,0:44:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能让你活下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.52,0:45:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆听从那个Festum说的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.97,0:45:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然绝对不能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.55,0:45:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.75,0:45:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.67,0:45:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵从我们的核心的引导吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.34,0:45:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去亚尔维斯住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.27,0:45:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.58,0:45:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.02,0:45:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽明明哪都不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.22,0:45:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去医院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.05,0:45:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.69,0:45:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要救总士
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.89,0:45:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.97,0:45:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外觉得天空很美的人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.42,0:45:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.40,0:45:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么觉得的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.32,0:45:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空很美
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.20,0:45:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是这么认为的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.24,0:46:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看不见天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.34,0:46:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要什么都看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.20,0:46:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代替我的手指会传递给我眼前的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.15,0:46:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.01,0:46:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士希望你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.33,0:46:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.55,0:46:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是你去向你的星核传达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.16,0:46:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.53,0:46:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.72,0:46:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们创造不了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.02,0:46:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在逃避痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.46,0:46:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把过错全归咎于他人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.69,0:46:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没考虑怎么消除痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.79,0:46:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是让你们做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.59,0:46:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的选择是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.46,0:46:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.23,0:46:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.65,0:47:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于知道了 他们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.99,0:47:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.46,0:47:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.33,0:47:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让你解脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.23,0:47:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.02,0:47:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再看到蓝天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.12,0:47:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所掌握的信息全都已经传达给了星核
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.83,0:47:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要叫我传达什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.66,0:47:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你传达了你不想战斗的心情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.40,0:47:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.86,0:47:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核对我来说 就好比你们所说的神一样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.39,0:47:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神是无法违抗的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.77,0:47:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 核心正在死去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.02,0:47:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不和人类战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.14,0:47:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不希望和你们一样 与世界为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.81,0:47:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么做的话 我就不再是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.04,0:48:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…要是按你说的做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.95,0:48:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.35,0:48:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.46,0:48:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过渴望与敌人对话的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.44,0:48:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给敌人建墓碑的还是头一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.52,0:48:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬也想要传达给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.76,0:48:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家悲伤的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.77,0:48:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.34,0:48:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.71,0:48:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你可以背负同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.00,0:48:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敌人的死只能铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.16,0:48:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.46,0:48:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人类也战斗过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.02,0:49:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.70,0:49:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只有你才能办到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.29,0:49:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕噢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.96,0:49:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.31,0:49:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替者能减轻核心的负荷的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.06,0:49:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就几周时间已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.70,0:49:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到以欧洛斯型为主的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.53,0:49:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大规模的敌人正在集结
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.25,0:49:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测其将大量与战斗无关的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.90,0:50:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置于支配之下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.33,0:50:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连非战斗员都叫来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.63,0:50:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用周围个体为自己作战
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.66,0:50:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是欧洛斯型的本质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.04,0:50:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数量的大军
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.98,0:50:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.48,0:50:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打赢了还会有下一批过来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.43,0:50:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直捣敌军星核了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.90,0:50:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.30,0:50:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据船上的资料和来主操所说的话来看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.03,0:50:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行中的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.69,0:50:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是敌方的星核
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.20,0:50:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题己方的战力和攻击方式
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.85,0:50:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经为了救这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.30,0:50:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说实行了叫做L计划的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.73,0:50:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们原人类军
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.74,0:50:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐同样的无人船
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.50,0:50:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引开敌人并消灭敌方星核
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.61,0:50:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什么手段
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.14,0:50:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地撤除人员
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.69,0:50:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用船上的芬里厄
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.69,0:50:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(378,438)}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.64,0:50:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将敌人炸得片甲不留
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.03,0:51:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敌人包围的状态下是不可能逃得出的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.03,0:51:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.13,0:51:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军的攻击 造出了那样的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.72,0:51:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.87,0:51:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾被当做弃子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.45,0:51:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被岛拯救了的这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.74,0:51:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我等的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.16,0:51:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许你们使用那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.25,0:51:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.39,0:51:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是为了牺牲各位
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.11,0:51:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能重蹈L计划的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.77,0:51:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我们来寻求对话了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.80,0:51:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上第一个自然受胎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.80,0:51:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据皆城乙姬对星核生与死的习得后
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.95,0:51:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先诞生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对皆城总士来说
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.55,0:51:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是未知的 与星核一样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.37,0:52:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽也是平时都处在CROSSING状态
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.15,0:52:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是岛上的星核本身
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.09,0:52:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.23,0:52:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 让美羽去谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.82,0:52:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.98,0:52:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.00,0:52:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 快投降
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.54,0:52:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.16,0:52:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去让战争停止
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.00,0:52:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核不听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.34,0:52:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.65,0:52:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空很美
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.42,0:52:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被命令 像人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.32,0:52:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得天空很美的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.61,0:52:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点被剥夺了会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.86,0:53:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去告诉你的神
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.27,0:53:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的妈妈也治不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.20,0:53:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她懂…我们的语言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.52,0:53:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美羽一起的话可以对话噢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.87,0:53:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是希望 真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.97,0:53:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…士…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.89,0:53:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.62,0:54:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.41,0:54:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈 前辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.80,0:54:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.46,0:54:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晖
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.43,0:55:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.87,0:55:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.32,0:55:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她才能向星核传达
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.82,0:55:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他们的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.46,0:55:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.78,0:55:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.26,0:55:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.98,0:55:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.70,0:55:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.57,0:55:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所封闭起来的门
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.95,0:55:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.94,0:55:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.33,0:55:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.84,0:55:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的星核这么命令的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.00,0:55:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家生活的地方大家一起保护
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.20,0:55:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.08,0:55:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保护了总士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.64,0:55:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为星核的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 只是不想他消失
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.31,0:55:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 星核在召唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.15,0:55:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快反抗你的神
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.57,0:55:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.96,0:56:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是Mark Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.33,0:56:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是为此 才把我化作人形的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.81,0:56:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.12,0:56:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽还能说更多噢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.18,0:56:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 只有你才能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.81,0:56:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.54,0:56:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把美羽带到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.42,0:56:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别从我身边夺走美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.55,0:56:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 一直在封闭着他
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.87,0:56:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.72,0:57:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.97,0:57:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.34,0:57:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这是你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.55,0:57:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让保存液和核心同步
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.34,0:57:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.94,0:57:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.36,0:57:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.65,0:57:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 求你了快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.76,0:57:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选择那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.83,0:57:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味地只会增加痛苦的神
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.85,0:57:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是去反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.47,0:57:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制止住装置解体
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.12,0:57:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.69,0:58:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司学长
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.78,0:58:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要放手噢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.36,0:58:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.51,0:58:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不是说过要用机体称呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.08,0:58:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司学长不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.85,0:58:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说学长你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.63,0:58:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的工作还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.82,0:58:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 去保护同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.52,0:58:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.30,0:58:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里厄启动认证
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.46,0:58:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行需要认证
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.56,0:58:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.35,0:58:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不用 我还在…这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.09,0:59:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晖
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.14,0:59:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.49,0:59:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…过来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.37,0:59:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是敌人的同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.00,0:59:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.31,0:59:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.96,0:59:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.70,0:59:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.25,1:00:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Vier
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.57,1:00:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.29,1:00:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才是 诞生在我们这边的可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.46,1:00:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的希望
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.76,1:00:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.44,1:01:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上Fafner了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.18,1:01:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.77,1:01:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.73,1:01:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 卡农
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.80,1:01:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.09,1:01:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死的就我一个足够了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.31,1:01:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.36,1:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.28,1:02:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逃离战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.03,1:02:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要战斗的 只有你们而已
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.60,1:02:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明 能够阻止的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.10,1:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.51,1:02:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.20,1:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不想你们消失的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.60,1:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然什么都诞生不了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.68,1:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.62,1:03:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我关在这也不会产生什么可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.17,1:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你知道战斗的方法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.90,1:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已放弃斗争了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.82,1:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个星核的状态
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.65,1:03:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是原先所追求的可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.66,1:03:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有疼痛增加了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.86,1:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的疼痛由我承受就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.74,1:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城总士的话或许就能办到吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.53,1:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.99,1:03:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛是皆城总士的祝福
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.04,1:03:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命是皆城乙姬的祝福
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.94,1:03:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么祝福世界
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.53,1:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我说这些
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.81,1:03:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在星核不在的情况下期望获得存在的首个个体
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.07,1:04:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何存在于此
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.31,1:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.90,1:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看天空
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.62,1:04:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是尽是悲伤
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.98,1:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经受不了自己的存在了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.36,1:04:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除大家的痛苦后
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.52,1:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让皆城总士和一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.46,1:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.61,1:04:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.32,1:04:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了Festum的大脑
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.36,1:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸妈妈消失时一样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.60,1:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还觉得二人还活在某处
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.04,1:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果哪都没有他们
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.63,1:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.31,1:04:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么爸爸妈妈会回来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.49,1:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把玄关的灯开着
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.71,1:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不让放灯笼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.44,1:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶也上了年纪了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.98,1:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是也不在了就只有我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.76,1:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在谁都不会回来的家中
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.19,1:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.95,1:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.05,1:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.68,1:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无人状态下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.88,1:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从机体的核心发来操纵数据
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.08,1:05:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西没有核心
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.85,1:05:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.15,1:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做Mark Nicht的时候拿掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.32,1:05:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心让机体动了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.72,1:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员仍显示是甲洋
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.66,1:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日井甲洋回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.42,1:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己作为机体的核心
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.47,1:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为保护这座岛
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.16,1:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽聊了很多噢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.87,1:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都聊了些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.87,1:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都很疼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.61,1:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行为是作为一个母亲应当的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.39,1:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子可不会这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.23,1:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想保护她的心情传达到了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.69,1:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.51,1:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽说了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.52,1:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是真的消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.50,1:06:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有机会回来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.79,1:06:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.40,1:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要持续到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.48,1:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们难道是为了被剥夺才在这座岛上的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.64,1:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让人夺去的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.74,1:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算赌上我的性命
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.99,1:06:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个抱着婴儿的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.29,1:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说她有多痛苦又有多开心
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.80,1:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和美羽说噢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.08,1:06:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道在说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.75,1:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬和岛上的星核的经验
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.00,1:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能传达给星核
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.43,1:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的能让敌方撤退吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.86,1:06:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅几分钟内
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.38,1:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门确认到大量通过CROSSING的信息交流
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.58,1:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了未知的无限数的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.21,1:06:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极其复杂的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.18,1:06:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类还未彻底知晓宇宙中存在的数目
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.47,1:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是其中一种
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.36,1:07:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日野美羽很自然地就理解了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.58,1:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像记住母语一样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.10,1:07:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还发挥了连皆城乙姬都没有的影响力
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.52,1:07:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门的开发者要是还在这的话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.78,1:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会相当高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.58,1:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.78,1:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能理解敌方的命令系统
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.13,1:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把来自欧洛斯型的命令改写
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.48,1:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和命令 信息什么的概念上就不同吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.01,1:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他坚持交谈这个说法
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.34,1:07:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在诉说对方的感性
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.21,1:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们不同性质的Festum的感性
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.83,1:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是代替消灭敌人的手段吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.47,1:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这就是本次作战的全部
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.42,1:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是在岛的保护范围内利用那艘无人船
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.50,1:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻入敌方根据地的战术啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.27,1:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且目的是在于…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.16,1:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让日野美羽和敌方星核对话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.90,1:07:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的指挥由沟口负责
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.88,1:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船的指挥由我来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.23,1:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子小姐怎么说
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母女一起上船
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.64,1:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信全员都能平安回归
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.92,1:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要敌人还要持续战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.19,1:08:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早我们的核心会死去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.40,1:08:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛会被夺走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.24,1:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们来说已经是最后了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.60,1:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是最大的希望
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.00,1:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很了不起呢 保
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.42,1:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有逃避Fafner
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.87,1:08:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.78,1:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在逃避让我丧失女儿和女婿的这东西
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.09,1:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对数螺旋结成
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.65,1:08:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动成功
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.82,1:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们父母留下的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.11,1:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能保护他们俩
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.48,1:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在确定本次作战的先遣人员
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.52,1:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击部队
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.75,1:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤剑司
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.92,1:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咲良
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.00,1:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尾里奈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.10,1:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尾晖
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.68,1:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫部队
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.79,1:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见真矢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.82,1:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间卡农
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.93,1:09:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马广登
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.47,1:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.34,1:09:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.03,1:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军袭来后的同时
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.38,1:09:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击部队就离开岛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.56,1:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向敌方大本营发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.89,1:09:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.96,1:09:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为全员的生还和重逢祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.60,1:09:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去消除疼痛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.08,1:09:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vier发来了出击许可的请求
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.28,1:09:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.29,1:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Vier要出击了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.92,1:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次苍穹作战开始
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.25,1:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.43,1:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持圆顶模式
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.87,1:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制程序启动开始
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.13,1:10:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机上前迎击
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.98,1:10:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.04,1:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定地点没有敌机出现
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.18,1:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.33,1:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果目标有误的话
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.91,1:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛就会…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.57,1:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.79,1:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.47,1:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是皆城总士托付给我们的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.08,1:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么在
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.45,1:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据对照
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.17,1:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军航母伯利亚欧斯
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.17,1:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(391,438)}Bollearios
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.39,1:11:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用了伪装镜面和防护壁
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.56,1:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙宫岛的防御系统…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.06,1:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用从我们这学到的技术来侵略我们吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.26,1:11:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持深度
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.28,1:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner准备出击
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.83,1:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距敌方防护壁 距离200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.14,1:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero Fafner 出击
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.06,1:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏不了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.14,1:12:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让防护壁与波长相符
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.25,1:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.51,1:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敌方防护壁
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.21,1:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Drei 出击
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.71,1:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-1至T-3 开炮
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.43,1:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水雷支援
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.90,1:12:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Acht 出击
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.47,1:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水雷支援
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.31,1:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认航母上出现因敌方星核产生的力场
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.44,1:13:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日野母女叫来这里
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.31,1:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的岛…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.93,1:14:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这憎恶感…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.30,1:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 星核
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.60,1:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我背负这种东西
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.36,1:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.88,1:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方力场从上空逼近
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.18,1:15:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想吞噬这座岛
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.88,1:15:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆顶防护壁展开
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.59,1:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛屿航行速度最大 全速掉头
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.59,1:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕噢 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.37,1:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化 开始
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.13,1:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我谁都救不了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.81,1:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来…我来保护大家
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.71,1:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一骑还来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.52,1:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.43,1:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样交谈不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.74,1:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.66,1:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太危险了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.80,1:16:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这是唯一可能的突破手段
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.05,1:16:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用Fafner牵制敌军
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.70,1:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水雷支援
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.04,1:16:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰在敌军后方浮上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.49,1:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开辟对话的通路
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.44,1:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑的…母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.67,1:17:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我与星核同步
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.27,1:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来维持核心的生命
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.75,1:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.95,1:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.57,1:17:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我 最后的可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.00,1:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是以前的核心告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.99,1:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这岛是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.57,1:18:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近范围没有敌机
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.63,1:18:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快浮上
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.26,1:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.20,1:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.58,1:19:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.34,1:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够努力的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.85,1:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.02,1:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.40,1:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么什么都不去阻止
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.04,1:20:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.52,1:20:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只想要将讨厌的东西全部消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.96,1:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星核本可重获新生的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.56,1:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们人类的火焰把一切都改变了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.82,1:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去再改变一次
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.90,1:20:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士把赌注押在你身上
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.10,1:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你和我们见面
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.27,1:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变你们
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.95,1:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经被选择好了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.59,1:21:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了你们
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.65,1:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此要怎么改变
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.94,1:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.61,1:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾让总士受伤
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.76,1:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直让他背负着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.07,1:21:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他还是相信了我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.64,1:21:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.82,1:21:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.82,1:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.31,1:21:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去选择吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.37,1:21:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论几次
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.88,1:21:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算感到悲伤也不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.06,1:21:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择存在于此吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.06,1:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要消失 一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.79,1:22:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核 我已经…不想再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.70,1:22:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.97,1:22:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说吧 天空很美的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.33,1:22:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽也很高兴 能降生于此
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.89,1:22:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.36,1:22:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾诺拉512维持线路飞来
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.36,1:22:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(232,438)}Enola
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.71,1:22:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝通讯 没有回应
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.89,1:22:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要连我们一同消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.44,1:22:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.06,1:22:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为人类的我们
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.58,1:23:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.66,1:23:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.90,1:23:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.38,1:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让她消失 星核
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.36,1:24:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也觉得很美
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.40,1:24:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起 降生吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.75,1:24:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真正的永别了呢 小芹
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.68,1:24:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.46,1:24:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.97,1:24:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人类的火焰 停止了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.91,1:25:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 救救我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.67,1:25:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心撑过了成长期
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.96,1:25:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.80,1:25:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁输出功率以及人工生态圈机能均未降低
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.01,1:25:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无放射能污染的征兆
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.26,1:25:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.69,1:25:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后的最后
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.68,1:25:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是岛保护了我们
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.16,1:25:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛正在消失
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.20,1:25:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核变成大气了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.75,1:25:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.93,1:25:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的敌人要诞生了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.39,1:25:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是选择中的一项
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.84,1:25:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确信的是现在这颗星球
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.21,1:26:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为他们的故乡了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.49,1:26:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是蓝天啊 小芹
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.66,1:26:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.80,1:26:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.03,1:26:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想带走阻碍你欣赏天空的障碍
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.05,1:26:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自做出这种事 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.28,1:26:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你能看见天空我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.82,1:26:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此中断了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.14,1:26:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将来说不定会到达
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.36,1:26:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他获得新生的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.96,1:27:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你若看不见天空就太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.57,1:27:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他最后的思考
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.17,1:27:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.10,1:27:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在庇护我的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.85,1:27:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从星核的同时也在抵抗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.49,1:27:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是同化
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.75,1:27:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是引导存在和谐共存
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.79,1:27:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.30,1:27:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.47,1:27:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}谢谢你 一骑
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.84,1:27:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}保护了岛
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.23,1:27:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}保护了我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.78,1:27:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.29,1:27:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}欢迎回来 总士
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.22,1:27:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界充满了无尽的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.34,1:28:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那一切都有其归宿
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.25,1:28:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我愿意去相信
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.74,1:28:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在拥有归宿的最好的安宁
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.23,1:28:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正是为此才存在于此的吧

